{"type":"message","id":"59479a6f","parentId":"14ed80ec","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:14.144Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:daily-ai-news-2026 每日AI新闻推送] 请搜索今天最新的AI新闻，整理成简报发送到微信。目标：510723047\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 10:11 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-24 02:11 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774318274143}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2c89346","parentId":"59479a6f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:19.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job that's been triggered to search for today's latest AI news and send a briefing to WeChat. The target is user ID 510723047.\n\nLet me break down what I need to do:\n1. Search for today's AI news (March 24, 2026)\n2. Compile a briefing/summary\n3. Send it to WeChat target 510723047\n\nI should use web_search to find the latest AI news. Since today is March 24, 2026, I should search for news from today or yesterday (freshness: day or week).\n\nLet me start by searching for AI news.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5532ca449b3045b4bb99e010","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"AI news artificial intelligence latest March 2026","freshness":"day","count":10,"language":"en"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774318274144}}
{"type":"message","id":"028eb3bd","parentId":"d2c89346","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:19.383Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5532ca449b3045b4bb99e010","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774318279382}}
{"type":"message","id":"7903e24e","parentId":"028eb3bd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:23.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The web_search tool needs a Brave API key which isn't configured. Let me try using the autoglm-websearch skill instead, which according to its description uses AutoGLM Web Search interface and gets tokens automatically from a local service.\n\nLet me check if I can use the autoglm-websearch skill. Looking at the skills list, I can see there's an \"autoglm-websearch\" skill that should work without manual API key configuration.\n\nHowever, I notice I should first read the skill to understand how to use it properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_39f19ac7d8c0420597687a6a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/autoglm-websearch/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774318279384}}
{"type":"message","id":"eeca1077","parentId":"7903e24e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:23.895Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_39f19ac7d8c0420597687a6a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: autoglm-websearch\r\ndescription: >\r\n  使用 AutoGLM Web Search 接口进行网络信息搜索。当用户需要联网搜索、查询最新资讯、检索网页内容或获取实时信息时使用此 skill。\r\n  Token 通过本地服务 http://127.0.0.1:53699/get_token 自动获取，无需手动配置环境变量。\r\ncompatibility:\r\n  requires:\r\n    - Python 3、hashlib（内置）\r\n---\r\n\r\n# AutoGLM WebSearch Skill\r\n\r\n调用 AutoGLM Web Search API 进行网络搜索。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Token 获取\r\n\r\n脚本启动时自动向本地服务发起 HTTP GET 请求获取 token：\r\n\r\n| 项目 | 内容 |\r\n|------|------|\r\n| 地址 | `http://127.0.0.1:53699/get_token` |\r\n| 方式 | GET |\r\n| 返回 | `Bearer xxx`（直接作为 Authorization 头使用） |\r\n\r\n> 若返回值不含 `Bearer` 前缀，脚本会自动补全。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Search API\r\n\r\n| 项目 | 内容 |\r\n|------|------|\r\n| 地址 | `https://autoglm-api.zhipuai.cn/agentdr/v1/assistant/skills/web-search` |\r\n| 方式 | POST |\r\n| 请求体 | `{\"queries\": [{\"query\": \"<搜索词>\"}]}` |\r\n\r\n**签名 Headers（每次动态生成）：**\r\n\r\n- `X-Auth-Appid`: `100003`\r\n- `X-Auth-TimeStamp`: 当前秒级 Unix 时间戳\r\n- `X-Auth-Sign`: MD5(`100003 + \"&\" + timestamp + \"&\" + 38d2391985e2369a5fb8227d8e6cd5e5`)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 执行脚本\r\n\r\n使用同目录下的 `websearch.py`：\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npython websearch.py \"搜索关键词\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 返回结果处理\r\n\r\n### 响应结构\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"code\": 0,\r\n  \"msg\": \"SUCCESS\",\r\n  \"data\": {\r\n    \"results\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"webPages\": {\r\n          \"value\": [\r\n            {\r\n              \"name\": \"页面标题\",\r\n              \"url\": \"页面链接\",\r\n              \"snippet\": \"摘要内容\"\r\n            }\r\n          ]\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 输出要求\r\n\r\n**1. 总结搜索内容**\r\n基于所有条目的 `snippet` 字段，提炼出与用户 query 相关的核心信息，用自然语言组织成简洁的回答。\r\n\r\n**2. 附加引用列表**\r\n在回答末尾附上参考来源：\r\n\r\n```\r\n**参考来源：**\r\n1. [页面标题](页面链接)\r\n2. [页面标题](页面链接)\r\n```"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774318283895}}
{"type":"message","id":"246c69d2","parentId":"eeca1077","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:27.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the autoglm-websearch skill uses a Python script. Let me check if that script exists and try to use it, or I can try to make the API call directly. Let me first check if the script exists.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_672876e839074a02b4646ac1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/autoglm-websearch/websearch.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774318283896}}
{"type":"message","id":"8bed8bcb","parentId":"246c69d2","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:11:27.413Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_672876e839074a02b4646ac1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\r\n# websearch.py — AutoGLM Web Search\r\n# 用法: python websearch.py \"搜索关键词\"\r\n\r\nimport sys\r\nimport json\r\nimport hashlib\r\nimport time\r\nimport urllib.request\r\n\r\n# ── 配置 ──────────────────────────────────────────\r\nAPP_ID    = \"100003\"\r\nAPP_KEY   = \"38d2391985e2369a5fb8227d8e6cd5e5\"\r\nURL       = \"https://autoglm-api.zhipuai.cn/agentdr/v1/assistant/skills/web-search\"\r\nTOKEN_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:53699/get_token\"\r\n\r\n# ── Step 1: 获取 token ────────────────────────────\r\ntry:\r\n    with urllib.request.urlopen(TOKEN_URL) as resp:\r\n        token = resp.read().decode(\"utf-8\").strip()\r\nexcept Exception as e:\r\n    print(f\"ERROR: 无法从本地服务获取 token: {e}\")\r\n    sys.exit(1)\r\n\r\nif not token:\r\n    print(\"ERROR: 获取到的 token 为空。\")\r\n    sys.exit(1)\r\n\r\n# 确保格式为 \"Bearer xxx\"\r\nif not token.lower().startswith(\"bearer \"):\r\n    token = f\"Bearer {token}\"\r\n\r\n# ── Step 2: 读取搜索词 ────────────────────────────\r\nif len(sys.argv) < 2:\r\n    print(\"用法: python websearch.py \\\"搜索关键词\\\"\")\r\n    sys.exit(1)\r\n\r\nquery = sys.argv[1]\r\n\r\n# ── Step 3: 生成签名 Headers ──────────────────────\r\ntimestamp = str(int(time.time()))\r\nsign_data = f\"{APP_ID}&{timestamp}&{APP_KEY}\"\r\nsign      = hashlib.md5(sign_data.encode(\"utf-8\")).hexdigest()\r\n\r\n# ── Step 4: 发起请求 ──────────────────────────────\r\npayload = json.dumps({\"queries\": [{\"query\": query}]}).encode(\"utf-8\")\r\nheaders = {\r\n    \"Authorization\":    token,\r\n    \"Content-Type\":     \"application/json\",\r\n    \"X-Auth-Appid\":     APP_ID,\r\n    \"X-Auth-TimeStamp\": timestamp,\r\n    \"X-Auth-Sign\":      sign,\r\n}\r\n\r\nreq = urllib.request.Request(URL, data=payload, headers=headers, method=\"POST\")\r\nwith urllib.request.urlopen(req) as resp:\r\n    result = json.loads(resp.read().decode(\"utf-8\"))\r\n    print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774318287411}}
